n English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isFrozen\"><code>Object.isFrozen()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isSealed\"><code>Object.isSealed()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/keys\"><code>Object.keys()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/preventExtensions\"><code>Object.preventExtensions()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/seal\"><code>Object.seal()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><em><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/values\"><code>Object.values()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"> <div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Niestandardowy:</strong> This feature is non-standard and is not on a standards track. Do not use it on production sites facing the Web: it will not work for every user. There may also be large incompatibilities between implementations and the behavior may change in the future.</p></div></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"podsumowanie","title":"Podsumowanie","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Zwraca literał obiektowy reprezentujący kod źródłowy danego obiektu.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sk.c5.82adnia","title":"Składnia","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code>Object.toSource();\n<var>obj</var>.toSource();\n</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parametry","title":"Parametry","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Brak.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"opis","title":"Opis","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Metoda <code>toSource()</code> zwraca następujące wartości:</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>dla obiektu wbudowanego <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a> metoda <code>toSource()</code> zwraca następujący ciąg znaków, wskazujący na niedostępność kodu źródłowego:\n\n  <div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n   <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>native code<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n </li>\n <li>dla instancji <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object\"><code>Object</code></a> metoda <code>toSource()</code> zwraca ciąg reprezentujący ich kod źródłowy.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Metoda ta zazwyczaj jest używana wewnętrznie przez interpreter JavaScriptu, a nie bezpośrednio w kodzie. Można jednak wywołać <code>toSource()</code> podczas debugowania, by zbadać zawartość danego obiektu.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ady","title":"Przykłady","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"przyk.c5.82ad_zastosowanie_tosource","title":"Przykład: Zastosowanie <code>toSource()</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Poniższy kod definiuje typ obiektowy <code>Pies</code> i tworzy instancję <code>piesek</code> jako obiekt typu <code>Pies</code>:</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js  language-js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Pies</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">nazwa</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nazwa <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> nazwa<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token class-name\">Pies</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>prototype<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">toSource</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">Pies_toSource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token string\">'new Pies('</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token function\">uneval</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>nazwa<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">+</span> <span class=\"token string\">')'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Pies</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Joe'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">toSource</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// ---&gt; new  Pies(\"Joe\")</span></code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Przykład: Zastosowanie toSource()"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce","title":"Zobacz także","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array/toString\"><code>Array.prototype.toSource()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;— <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Array\"><code>Array</code></a> Object method.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean/toString\"><code>Boolean.prototype.toSource()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;— <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a> Object method.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/toString\"><code>Date.prototype.toSource()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;— <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date\"><code>Date</code></a> Object method.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function/toString\"><code>Function.prototype.toSource()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;— <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Function\"><code>Function</code></a> Object method.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number/toString\"><code>Number.prototype.toSource()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;— <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Number\"><code>Number</code></a> Object method.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp/toString\"><code>Regexp.prototype.toSource()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;— <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/RegExp\"><code>RegExp</code></a> Object method.</li>\n <li><a href=\"/pl/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String/toString\"><code>String.prototype.toSource()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;— <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>String</code></a> Object method.</li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Symbol/toString\"><code>Symbol.prototype.toSource()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg>&nbsp;— <a href=\"/pl/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Symbol\"><code>Symbol</code></a> Object method.</li>\n <li><code>Math.toSource()</code>&nbsp;— Returns the String \"Math\".</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Podsumowanie","id":"podsumowanie"},{"text":"Składnia","id":"sk.c5.82adnia"},{"text":"Opis","id":"opis"},{"text":"Przykłady","id":"przyk.c5.82ady"},{"text":"Zobacz także","id":"zobacz_tak.c5.bce"}],"summary":"Zwraca literał obiektowy reprezentujący kod źródłowy danego obiektu.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Object.prototype.toSource()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toSource()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toSource()","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toSource()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Object.prototype.toSource()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pl/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/object/tostring","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pl/conflicting/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/object/tostring/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"Object.prototype.toSource() | MDN","noIndexing":true}}